This directory contains all simulations used for NCV power evaluation.
I redid the scripts and the simulations on 22.10.2014 in order to organize the data and have clearer scripts and directories, so I might erase some of the old ones.



Names of files are self explanatory

Tbs: time since appearance of balanced polymorphism (1, 3 and 5 million years)

n100..n20: size of sample from each pop (Africa, Europe, Asia) [+1 chimp]

l3kb..l12kb: sequence length


neutral:neutral simulations (one set for each sequence length)



OBS: 23.10.2014

I am runnign script l6kb_simulations.r in dir tmp6 and l12kb_simulations.r in dir tmp12 (using source). It appears to be working. After I run it I can copy the simulations to this directory.

